Package fitness

Class Date

java.lang.Object
fitness.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
Date class deals with verifying all the dates used for Gym membership. Different methods work on checking or providing the correct date.
Author:
Tanvi Thigle, Leah Ranavat
